 S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 694\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37597,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/23\/imams-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":25680,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jama\u2019ah: Imams should supplicate for their congregants too","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe one who leads others in prayer should not supplicate only for himself to the exclusion of them. If he does so, he has betrayed them.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 357 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25703,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/29\/repeat-adhan-then-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":25680,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Adhan: Repeat the call to prayer, then supplicate","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 29, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, the callers to prayer have been favored over us.\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSay as they have said. When you have finished, ask Allah and you will receive.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"te